（料箱型机器人，主要用于仓库搬运操作）
Job responsibilities:

岗位职责：
1. Conduct preliminary project planning for the warehouse robot project and carry out various aspects of work, such as collecting robot related requirements/functions;

对仓库机器人项目进行前期项目规划，开展各方面工作，比如搜集机器人相关需求/功能；

2. Based on the characteristics of the project, be able to calculate relevant basic data, such as the daily number of inbound and outbound containers, weight, warehouse area, distance, etc;

针对项目的特点，能计算相关基础数据，每日出入库箱数，重量，仓库面积，距离等；

3. Configure relevant networks and other equipment based on the on-site situation of the warehouse; Check if the warehouse environment meets the requirements of robot project operation, such as building obstruction, ground flatness, shelf load capacity, etc. If not, coordinate with various departments to improve;

根据仓库现场情况，配置相关网络和其他设备；查看仓库环境是否符合机器人项目运行，比如建筑物遮挡，地面平整度，货架承载率等因素，如不符合的需协调各个部门改善；

4. Actively understand the mainstream models and latest technologies of material box robots in the market, screen the best suppliers, models and quantities, propose preliminary planning plans to the management, and continuously improve the plans;

积极了解市场上主流料箱机器人型号和***，筛选最优供应商，型号和数量，给管理层提出初步规划方案，并不断完善方案；

5. In daily work, operate robots and robot systems correctly to meet daily operational requirements;

机器人项目开始运作后，在日常工作中，须正确操作机器人和机器人系统，满足日常操作要求；

6. If robots don’t work, can be resolved in time or notified to the supplier for maintenance;

如机器人发生故障时能及时解决问题，或通知供应商维护，确保产线不停运； 

7. Record on-site feedback issues, analyze and summarize problems, and form a manual;

记录现场反馈问题，分析并总结问题，形成手册；

8. Continuously optimize process plans and actively improve according to customer requirements;
根据客户和公司要求能不断优化流程方案，积极改进；

9. Actively communicate with the logistics department internally and maintain smooth communication with suppliers externally;

对内与物流部积极沟通，对外与供应商保持沟通顺畅；

10. Complete other tasks assigned by the leader.

完成领导布置的其他任务。


